Swords

70
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,260
Spears

71
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:13,760
Paper Fans

72
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:15,760
Flying Guillotines

73
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,220
Threading needles

74
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:20,280
And Whatever Jackie Chan wants to use

